data.description: Single level home! 3 Bedroom, 1 bath with a 4th non-conforming bedroom. (garage was converted to a bedroom so can be used as a bedroom or garage) 2 sheds, fenced yard, centrally located. A little TLC and this home would be a cute home! New pad and carpet installed last week.  This property to be sold as is, where is.  The sellers will not do any repairs.  Call Lisa Engebretsen with Forefront Real Estate at (307) 262-9740.
